  "keyFeatures": [
    "Structured logging with message templates",
    "Rich log routing with logging rules and filters",
    "Multiple built-in targets (File, Console, EventLog, Database, etc.)",
    "Flexible layout system with 60+ layout renderers",
    "XML and programmatic configuration",
    "AOT (Ahead-of-Time) compilation compatible",
    "Cross-platform: .NET 6-10, .NET Standard 2.0/2.1, .NET Framework 3.5-4.8, Xamarin, Mono",
    "Target wrapper support (async, buffering, retry, fallback, filtering)",
    "ScopeContext for contextual logging (similar to log4j2 ThreadContext)",
    "Extensible via custom targets, layout renderers, and conditions"
  ],
